document_title: Rat poison poisoning: Symptoms, diagnosis and prevention
subsection_content:
Rat poison poisoning comes from the following causes:
Accidental inhalation.; Confusion with food.; Children do not know how to accidentally ingest it.; Family conflicts, pressure, psychological tension, etc. lead to suicide by drinking rat poison; Poisoned.
